window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Best-selling author L. E. Modesitt, Jr. begins his Ghost Books series with <i>Of Tangible Ghosts</i> in a strange alternate reality where ghosts are no longer mere superstition, but physical realities.</p> <p>When two real ghosts and the records of a murdered researcher enter the life of Johan Eschbach, the former spy and present professor finds himself caught with the secret of high-technology de-ghosting, and the whole world, including his former spymasters, try to turn Johan himself into another ghost.</p>"; 
